file_content.text: [You enter Jax Dumont's code and release the Republic agent Phalanx from his cell.]
What's going on? What kind of uniform is that?
Special Forces. It's the latest fashion for jailbreaks. Let's get out of here.
The lightsaber didn't give me away? Come, we have little time and we need to get moving.
I try to rescue you and you make fun of my clothes? Just move already!
An agent named Jax Dumont sent me. Get ready to run.
The important thing is, you're not getting a bomb put in your skull. Follow me.
All right, but I hope you're ready for a noisy exit. The guards here know what they're doing.
[This cell door is heavily reinforced. Whoever is inside isn't getting out.]
